  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Lucia checks her pocket watch. The thing is fueled by a mix of high-tech nonsense and Vampire blood. </i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>As her ship rounds the moon, the Vampires' space-fortress comes into view…</i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/b387e670da22e3a0cda4a6f0725af250.webp?t=1733569659\" width=717 height=34 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bullet Hell Deckbuilder</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Moon Watch mixes deckbuilding strategy and bullet hell action, where time itself becomes your weapon!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/52c3c790737487a7ba5124e4a8bf9b37.poster.avif?t=1733569659\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/52c3c790737487a7ba5124e4a8bf9b37.webm?t=1733569659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the flow of time to think strategically and weave impossible odds in your favor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenges to unlock new cards and characters with unique attacks and abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Refine your deck to build devastating combos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover rare relics that completely change your run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt the darkest threat the world, and the moon, has ever known.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/b387e670da22e3a0cda4a6f0725af250.webp?t=1733569659\" width=717 height=34 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wield Three Unique Characters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock  their specialized playstyles, decks, and powerful relics!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/3881197280ba9c0098ed8b16451c3ad3.avif?t=1733569659\" width=800 height=132 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lucia the Nun</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your go-to starter character! She uses garlic to control space and projectiles to attack enemies. Straightforward and dependable. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nina the Ninja</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A melee queen! Nina thrives in close combat with dashes to evade enemies and powerful sword slashes. She also has a “curse” ability to weaken foes, making her a great pick for those who love risk and reward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Encio the Engineer</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A creative powerhouse! Encio uses pinball ability to move around the level, relies on electricity and turrets as offense. Also has a “charm” ability that he can use to turn enemies against each other.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/b387e670da22e3a0cda4a6f0725af250.webp?t=1733569659\" width=717 height=34 /></span><i>This is it. </i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Our chance to strike back at the Vampire Lords who haunt our planet from above!</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/2d17ab81e78189081b433f186c4a848b.poster.avif?t=1733569659\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/2d17ab81e78189081b433f186c4a848b.webm?t=1733569659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Lucia checks her pocket watch. The thing is fueled by a mix of high-tech nonsense and Vampire blood. </i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>As her ship rounds the moon, the Vampires' space-fortress comes into view…</i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/b387e670da22e3a0cda4a6f0725af250.webp?t=1733569659\" width=717 height=34 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bullet Hell Deckbuilder</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Moon Watch mixes deckbuilding strategy and bullet hell action, where time itself becomes your weapon!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/52c3c790737487a7ba5124e4a8bf9b37.poster.avif?t=1733569659\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/52c3c790737487a7ba5124e4a8bf9b37.webm?t=1733569659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the flow of time to think strategically and weave impossible odds in your favor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenges to unlock new cards and characters with unique attacks and abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Refine your deck to build devastating combos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover rare relics that completely change your run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt the darkest threat the world, and the moon, has ever known.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878030/extras/b387e670da22e3a0cda4a6f0725af250.webp?t=173356